    "schema:description": "Metadata harvested directly from NCEI NOAA landing page JSON-LD by Claude Code. Converted to CDIF discovery profile: Property names prefixed with schema: namespace; Unprefixed properties assigned to unk: namespace (contentURL); @context set to CDIF prefix declarations (extra prefixes preserved); @type values normalized to arrays with schema: prefix; @id set from schema:url; schema:dateModified set from schema:datePublished; schema:identifier unwrapped from array; Distributions normalized; schema:creator wrapped in @list; Agent objects fixed (Person name synthesis, sameAs arrays). 2026-04-08: Removed @id from schema:identifier PropertyValue (was identical to root Dataset @id, causing JSON-LD framing to merge PropertyValue @type into Dataset)."
